  <brief_title>The Effect of Exercise on Blood Glucose Levels in Patients With Type 1 Diabetes: A Comparison of 3 Long-acting Insulins</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Assessment of the Impact of Performing Physical Exercise on the Maximum Plasma Glucose Decline in Subjects With Type 1 Diabetes Managed on a Basal Bolus Insulin Regimen: A Comparison of 3 Basal Insulin Treatments - Insulin Detemir, Insulin Glargine and NPH Insulin</official_title>
  <sponsors>
