  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Europe. The aim of this research is to assess the impact of three
      basal (long-acting) insulin treatments on blood glucose levels in people with type 1 diabetes
      when performing physical exercise.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
